by jakzal at 2014-09-11T20:37:10Z

Actually, I think it's solved in a wrong place. The errors are coming from [`XmlUtils::loadFile()`](https://github.com/symfony/symfony/blob/master/src/Symfony/Component/Config/Util/XmlUtils.php#L41). That's where `libxml_clear_errors()` should be called.

